0.3.0 -- 25-06-2015
-------------------

- Add support for masks.
- Add a simple `above_percentile` mask generator.
- Fix an issue with the amplitude max boundary.
- Implement Gibbs within Metropolis-Hastings.


0.2.0 -- 13-04-2015
-------------------

- Add some plots.
- Display the acceptance ratio for each iteration.
- Optimize heavily.


0.1.0 -- 01-02-2015
-------------------

- Initial implementation, without any optimization.
- Support user-defined line models.
- Add basic support for input FITS files.
